r /><br>When you are dating..... He likes to "discuss" things.<br /><br>When you are married ....He develops a "blank" stare.<br /><br><br /><br>When you are dating..... He calls you by name.<br /><br>When you are married ....He calls you "Hey" and refers to you when speaking to others as "She."','Men / Women',4031,'Dating Vs. Marriage');
